1
00:01:27,040 --> 00:01:35,760
[The Guardians]

2
00:01:36,120 --> 00:01:38,920
[Episode 16]

3
00:01:40,120 --> 00:01:40,930
Liang.

4
00:01:41,790 --> 00:01:42,930
It's Ms. Xian Biyun.

5
00:01:43,200 --> 00:01:44,210
Don't be afraid.

6
00:01:45,310 --> 00:01:46,380
Joseph.

7
00:01:47,590 --> 00:01:48,380
It's all my fault.

8
00:01:49,920 --> 00:01:50,850
It's all my fault.

9
00:01:50,870 --> 00:01:52,380
It's all my fault, Biyun.

10
00:01:55,840 --> 00:01:56,740
It's my fault

11
00:01:56,760 --> 00:01:58,690
for not staying by your side

12
00:02:00,230 --> 00:02:01,980
and letting you suffer such grievance.

13
00:02:05,480 --> 00:02:06,770
When I proposed,

14
00:02:08,470 --> 00:02:10,450
I promised to protect you well

15
00:02:10,470 --> 00:02:12,260
and not let you suffer
even the slightest harm.

16
00:02:13,750 --> 00:02:14,570
I never thought

17
00:02:15,240 --> 00:02:16,660
I'd break my word so soon.

18
00:02:19,400 --> 00:02:20,690
You already proposed?

19
00:02:22,360 --> 00:02:24,060
Biyun, did you say yes?

20
00:02:33,280 --> 00:02:34,260
I said yes.

21
00:02:38,000 --> 00:02:41,540
Joseph is already my fiance.

22
00:02:45,280 --> 00:02:46,540
That's wonderful.

23
00:02:52,710 --> 00:02:55,100
Biyun, don't be afraid.

24
00:02:55,680 --> 00:02:57,500
From now on,
Sanyangli will be your home.

25
00:02:57,520 --> 00:02:59,500
I'll arrange for you to move in.

26
00:03:01,680 --> 00:03:04,780
Mrs. Liang, isn't that inappropriate?

27
00:03:04,800 --> 00:03:06,660
Mr. Lee, you really don't know
how to care for girls.

28
00:03:07,080 --> 00:03:08,500
All the other experts' wives

29
00:03:08,520 --> 00:03:09,940
live in Sanyangli.

30
00:03:10,240 --> 00:03:11,410
That's right.

31
00:03:12,910 --> 00:03:15,660
She is now your fiancee.

32
00:03:16,080 --> 00:03:17,060
Biyun, if you move in,

33
00:03:17,080 --> 00:03:18,220
I'll have a mahjong partner.

34
00:03:19,800 --> 00:03:20,500
Well...

35
00:03:20,520 --> 00:03:21,730
That's not a problem.

36
00:03:26,360 --> 00:03:27,060
Come on, everyone.

37
00:03:27,750 --> 00:03:29,220
Let's raise our glasses together

38
00:03:29,630 --> 00:03:30,850
to congratulate Director Le

39
00:03:31,520 --> 00:03:32,780
on tying the knot.

40
00:03:38,080 --> 00:03:39,340
Congratulations.

41
00:03:39,360 --> 00:03:41,730
Come, cheers.

42
00:03:41,750 --> 00:03:43,060
Cheers.

43
00:03:51,360 --> 00:03:52,890
Bravo!

44
00:03:54,750 --> 00:03:55,780
Director Lee.

45
00:04:08,630 --> 00:04:09,220
Come.

46
00:04:13,520 --> 00:04:14,060
Sit down.

47
00:04:24,360 --> 00:04:25,220
What's going on?

48
00:04:26,510 --> 00:04:27,810
What do you mean?

49
00:04:28,480 --> 00:04:29,340
Your engagement.

50
00:04:30,480 --> 00:04:32,340
I was just about to explain to you.

51
00:04:32,360 --> 00:04:34,460
It's fake. Don't take it to heart.

52
00:04:34,480 --> 00:04:35,340
We were acting.

53
00:04:35,360 --> 00:04:36,020
Acting?

54
00:04:37,480 --> 00:04:38,580
Was it you wanting to act with her

55
00:04:38,600 --> 00:04:40,020
or did she pull you into acting?

56
00:04:40,680 --> 00:04:41,460
I pulled her.

57
00:04:46,800 --> 00:04:47,810
Let me ask you.

58
00:04:48,240 --> 00:04:50,020
What exactly is her purpose here?

59
00:04:50,680 --> 00:04:51,220
To protect me.

60
00:04:52,240 --> 00:04:54,580
And at the same time
cover for the two of us.

61
00:04:54,600 --> 00:04:56,020
One more person means more strength.

62
00:04:57,240 --> 00:04:59,020
Why did you make
this decision on your own?

63
00:04:59,040 --> 00:04:59,460
Do you know

64
00:04:59,480 --> 00:05:00,580
why Liang Jingyuan

65
00:05:00,600 --> 00:05:01,460
brought us here?

66
00:05:01,920 --> 00:05:03,580
On the surface, for work convenience.

67
00:05:03,600 --> 00:05:05,020
But in fact, to control us.

68
00:05:05,040 --> 00:05:05,580
Do you know

69
00:05:05,600 --> 00:05:07,580
how dangerous our current situation is?

70
00:05:07,920 --> 00:05:09,370
And what exactly can she assist us with?

71
00:05:09,390 --> 00:05:10,340
Do you know that she is...

72
00:05:13,830 --> 00:05:14,660
Do you know who she is?

73
00:05:16,920 --> 00:05:18,020
Ms. Xian.

74
00:05:22,830 --> 00:05:23,340
Alright.

75
00:06:13,240 --> 00:06:15,460
Ms. Xian is indeed a fine actress.

76
00:06:17,720 --> 00:06:18,700
So next,

77
00:06:19,800 --> 00:06:22,140
what play will you have Ding Yi
play in with you?

78
00:06:25,160 --> 00:06:26,700
I don't know what you're talking about.

79
00:06:30,360 --> 00:06:31,460
Let me put it this way,

80
00:06:32,830 --> 00:06:34,810
did you promise Ding Yi something

81
00:06:35,720 --> 00:06:37,050
so that he would help you like this?

82
00:06:39,360 --> 00:06:40,900
This was Ding Yi's own decision.

83
00:06:42,430 --> 00:06:43,410
Ms. Xian.

84
00:06:44,750 --> 00:06:47,540
It's not like you don't know
how Ding Yi feels about you.

85
00:06:48,600 --> 00:06:49,700
Gu Yangshan.

86
00:06:51,160 --> 00:06:53,020
Is that how you judge people?

87
00:06:54,360 --> 00:06:56,340
Ding Yi's no longer what he used to be.

88
00:06:57,680 --> 00:06:59,660
Neither you nor I can control his mind.

89
00:07:01,360 --> 00:07:02,170
Ms. Xian.

90
00:07:03,800 --> 00:07:04,580
Ding Yi

91
00:07:05,800 --> 00:07:07,220
is my brother.

92
00:07:07,920 --> 00:07:09,900
I know he's no longer what he once was.

93
00:07:10,920 --> 00:07:13,370
But I also won't allow him

94
00:07:14,390 --> 00:07:16,140
to be used by anyone.

95
00:07:33,950 --> 00:07:34,490
Ms. Xian.

96
00:07:37,070 --> 00:07:37,700
Director Liang.

97
00:07:39,160 --> 00:07:41,370
Charlie is being derelict in his duty.

98
00:07:42,390 --> 00:07:44,700
He's not even helping you
with your luggage.

99
00:07:45,040 --> 00:07:47,020
Charlie is Mr. Lee's personal assistant,

100
00:07:47,160 --> 00:07:48,340
not mine.

101
00:07:48,480 --> 00:07:49,900
That's not part of his job.

102
00:07:51,040 --> 00:07:51,580
I'll help you.

103
00:07:55,390 --> 00:07:56,930
Thank you, Director Liang.

104
00:07:58,120 --> 00:07:59,370
You're too polite, Ms. Xian.

105
00:08:00,830 --> 00:08:01,810
If we're talking about thanks,

106
00:08:01,830 --> 00:08:03,660
it should be me thanking you.

107
00:08:04,310 --> 00:08:05,410
Yin told me

108
00:08:05,950 --> 00:08:08,220
that my smooth return
to Shanghai this time

109
00:08:09,120 --> 00:08:11,580
was all thanks to Mr. Lee's
and your help.

110
00:08:13,240 --> 00:08:14,980
You flatter me, Director Liang.

111
00:08:15,000 --> 00:08:16,900
It was because of Yin
pulling connections.

112
00:08:17,270 --> 00:08:18,540
I didn't do much to help.

113
00:08:18,560 --> 00:08:19,370
No need to take it to heart.

114
00:08:21,120 --> 00:08:22,660
I'm very clear about

115
00:08:23,430 --> 00:08:24,780
who can do what kind of thing

116
00:08:25,720 --> 00:08:27,140
and who can give what kind of help.

117
00:08:28,480 --> 00:08:29,580
This favor

118
00:08:30,160 --> 00:08:31,250
should still be credited

119
00:08:31,270 --> 00:08:33,650
to you and Director Lee.

120
00:08:34,910 --> 00:08:35,460
Rest assured.

121
00:08:36,750 --> 00:08:39,890
I will absolutely know my limits,

122
00:08:39,910 --> 00:08:41,220
unlike Mr. Takeda.

123
00:08:41,240 --> 00:08:42,700
I won't end up like him.

124
00:08:44,270 --> 00:08:45,770
That was his work matter.

125
00:08:46,670 --> 00:08:47,370
I wouldn't know about it.

126
00:08:49,840 --> 00:08:50,700
Director Liang.

127
00:08:51,440 --> 00:08:52,890
We're old acquaintances now.

128
00:08:54,320 --> 00:08:57,010
I hope that in the future,

129
00:08:57,030 --> 00:08:58,650
you'll take good care of Mr. Lee.

130
00:08:59,960 --> 00:09:01,180
You already said
we're old acquaintances.

131
00:09:01,200 --> 00:09:02,890
Saying such things is silly.

132
00:09:04,600 --> 00:09:06,980
Director Lee is Grand Duke
Tonoji's adopted son.

133
00:09:07,480 --> 00:09:08,850
I must rely on him.

134
00:09:09,910 --> 00:09:10,650
Ms. Xian,

135
00:09:10,670 --> 00:09:12,060
if there's a chance in the future,

136
00:09:12,080 --> 00:09:14,370
please put in a good word for me
with Director Lee.

137
00:09:15,510 --> 00:09:16,890
Director Liang,

138
00:09:16,910 --> 00:09:18,130
you think too highly of me.

139
00:09:18,840 --> 00:09:20,250
I have no say over Mr. Lee.

140
00:09:21,000 --> 00:09:23,010
I'm just a washed-up actress,

141
00:09:23,510 --> 00:09:25,340
unable to make it out there anymore.

142
00:09:25,360 --> 00:09:27,850
It's only because of a bit of kindness
from Mr. Lee toward me

143
00:09:29,120 --> 00:09:30,730
that I came to seek refuge with him.

144
00:09:35,030 --> 00:09:37,010
Ms. Xian, you're far too modest.

145
00:09:44,270 --> 00:09:45,730
I remember back then,

146
00:09:46,630 --> 00:09:49,530
you managed to send
those rioting students

147
00:09:49,550 --> 00:09:52,010
out of Shanghai at such a young age.

148
00:09:53,750 --> 00:09:56,700
I've always kept that in mind.

149
00:10:00,870 --> 00:10:03,130
Who hasn't done foolish things
in their youth?

150
00:10:05,910 --> 00:10:07,250
Haven't you, Director Liang?

151
00:10:10,910 --> 00:10:12,610
I was at the height of my fame.

152
00:10:12,630 --> 00:10:14,250
Everyone would show me some respect.

153
00:10:16,840 --> 00:10:18,700
Was it really just showing respect?

154
00:10:19,600 --> 00:10:20,370
What do you mean?

155
00:10:33,910 --> 00:10:34,530
Biyun.

156
00:10:36,240 --> 00:10:37,010
Biyun.

157
00:10:39,480 --> 00:10:40,420
Biyun.

158
00:10:40,440 --> 00:10:41,580
Be careful.

159
00:10:42,200 --> 00:10:42,890
Joseph.

160
00:10:43,320 --> 00:10:44,420
Are you alright?

161
00:10:44,670 --> 00:10:45,420
I'm here.

162
00:10:47,270 --> 00:10:48,180
Biyun.

163
00:10:49,270 --> 00:10:50,130
Is that you?

164
00:10:50,150 --> 00:10:51,340
It's me.

165
00:10:51,360 --> 00:10:52,180
I'm right here.

166
00:10:54,840 --> 00:10:55,300
Then...

167
00:10:56,240 --> 00:10:56,700
This is...

168
00:10:56,720 --> 00:10:57,650
Liang Jingyuan.

169
00:11:01,240 --> 00:11:02,690
Pardon me, Director Liang.

170
00:11:04,710 --> 00:11:05,460
But,

171
00:11:05,950 --> 00:11:06,690
Director Liang,

172
00:11:07,160 --> 00:11:08,980
why are you here as well?

173
00:11:09,760 --> 00:11:11,220
Why did you come out alone?

174
00:11:13,790 --> 00:11:15,890
I noticed you hadn't been home.

175
00:11:16,400 --> 00:11:17,620
I was worried.

176
00:11:18,240 --> 00:11:18,890
So,

177
00:11:19,910 --> 00:11:21,050
I had to come look for you.

178
00:11:22,880 --> 00:11:24,410
Just now, Director Liang

179
00:11:24,430 --> 00:11:25,650
helped me carry my luggage,

180
00:11:26,480 --> 00:11:28,570
and we chatted briefly at the door.

181
00:11:31,070 --> 00:11:33,460
I must say,
Director Liang is thoughtful.

182
00:11:35,360 --> 00:11:36,100
Thank you.

183
00:11:36,120 --> 00:11:36,980
You're welcome.

184
00:11:38,040 --> 00:11:38,690
But,

185
00:11:39,240 --> 00:11:40,100
I'm to blame.

186
00:11:41,000 --> 00:11:41,930
I was careless.

187
00:11:43,190 --> 00:11:43,930
Charlie.

188
00:11:47,360 --> 00:11:48,100
Charlie.

189
00:11:53,710 --> 00:11:54,170
Charlie.

190
00:11:56,000 --> 00:11:56,810
Charlie!

191
00:12:04,120 --> 00:12:05,100
Aren't I just fine?

192
00:12:19,240 --> 00:12:20,220
Director Liang.

193
00:12:20,590 --> 00:12:21,570
My apologies.

194
00:12:24,590 --> 00:12:25,690
Where did you go?

195
00:12:27,000 --> 00:12:28,340
Mr. Lee,

196
00:12:28,360 --> 00:12:30,930
I was tidying up Ms. Xian's room.

197
00:12:31,360 --> 00:12:33,570
Ms. Xian, I'm really sorry.

198
00:12:33,590 --> 00:12:36,220
In the future, leave
this sort of thing to me.

199
00:12:37,710 --> 00:12:38,570
It's alright.

200
00:12:40,190 --> 00:12:40,980
From now on,

201
00:12:41,310 --> 00:12:43,220
you don't need to bother with me.

202
00:12:43,310 --> 00:12:44,500
Just take good care of Mr. Lee.

203
00:12:46,590 --> 00:12:47,570
Don't let it happen again.

204
00:12:49,480 --> 00:12:50,930
Yes, Mr. Lee.

205
00:12:53,070 --> 00:12:53,810
Everyone,

206
00:12:55,120 --> 00:12:56,220
you've all worked hard today.

207
00:12:56,240 --> 00:12:57,570
It's getting late.

208
00:12:57,590 --> 00:12:58,690
Rest early.

209
00:12:58,710 --> 00:12:59,570
I'll take my leave now.

210
00:13:05,240 --> 00:13:05,930
Director Lee.

211
00:13:09,480 --> 00:13:10,860
The roads in Sanyangli are tricky.

212
00:13:11,520 --> 00:13:13,860
Don't come out alone at night

213
00:13:14,830 --> 00:13:16,690
lest you fall into my arms again.

214
00:13:19,400 --> 00:13:19,980
See you.

215
00:13:28,360 --> 00:13:30,570
Careful, the step.

216
00:13:42,360 --> 00:13:44,220
What did Liang Jingyuan mean just now?

217
00:13:44,240 --> 00:13:45,690
You fell into his arms?

218
00:13:46,120 --> 00:13:47,570
I didn't mean to.

219
00:13:47,590 --> 00:13:48,650
I really tripped.

220
00:13:48,670 --> 00:13:49,340
Now he's already

221
00:13:49,360 --> 00:13:50,500
starting to suspect the three of us,

222
00:13:50,520 --> 00:13:51,100
you understand?

223
00:13:51,520 --> 00:13:53,220
This is the result of you
acting on your own.

224
00:13:53,830 --> 00:13:54,460
Before you do anything,

225
00:13:54,480 --> 00:13:55,340
can you tell me first

226
00:13:55,360 --> 00:13:56,570
and discuss it with me?

227
00:13:56,590 --> 00:13:58,460
In other people's eyes, I'm your eyes.

228
00:13:58,480 --> 00:14:00,460
I have to be by your side, understood?

229
00:14:20,400 --> 00:14:21,170
Ms. Xian.

230
00:14:21,190 --> 00:14:23,170
Let me take you up to see your room.

231
00:14:26,640 --> 00:14:27,170
Let's go.

232
00:14:29,950 --> 00:14:30,570
Let's go.

233
00:14:38,190 --> 00:14:39,290
Take care, Ms. Xian.

234
00:14:49,710 --> 00:14:51,570
This room, here.

235
00:15:05,120 --> 00:15:07,340
I'll put your luggage here for you.

236
00:15:11,880 --> 00:15:12,930
Oh right, Ms. Xian,

237
00:15:12,950 --> 00:15:14,620
see if there's anything you need.

238
00:15:14,640 --> 00:15:15,740
Just tell me.

239
00:15:15,760 --> 00:15:17,100
I'll have them get it ready.

240
00:15:23,480 --> 00:15:24,220
Ms. Xian,

241
00:15:25,070 --> 00:15:26,460
you came looking for me so urgently.

242
00:15:26,480 --> 00:15:28,220
Did you run into some trouble?

243
00:15:28,480 --> 00:15:29,340
I can help you.

244
00:15:32,360 --> 00:15:35,050
You were too impulsive just now.

245
00:15:38,590 --> 00:15:41,460
I saw him pestering you non-stop,

246
00:15:41,710 --> 00:15:43,740
so I thought I'd help you out.

247
00:15:45,480 --> 00:15:47,050
A blind man

248
00:15:47,070 --> 00:15:48,860
going out alone at night
to find someone.

249
00:15:49,590 --> 00:15:50,860
Wouldn't he find it suspicious?

250
00:15:51,480 --> 00:15:54,220
The two of us are an engaged couple.

251
00:15:54,240 --> 00:15:56,570
So it's only natural
that I'd be worried about you.

252
00:16:00,710 --> 00:16:01,980
I was wrong.

253
00:16:02,240 --> 00:16:03,460
I'll be more careful next time.

254
00:16:06,360 --> 00:16:06,930
It's late.

255
00:16:07,950 --> 00:16:08,740
Get some rest early.

256
00:16:10,480 --> 00:16:12,980
Alright, you rest early too.

257
00:16:13,310 --> 00:16:14,050
I'll head off.

258
00:16:16,790 --> 00:16:17,650
Ding Yi.

259
00:16:23,790 --> 00:16:24,690
Ms. Xian.

260
00:16:24,710 --> 00:16:27,460
Tomorrow, after I enter Sanyangli,

261
00:16:28,120 --> 00:16:30,100
it's very likely I'll lose my freedom

262
00:16:30,590 --> 00:16:32,100
and be unable to contact you.

263
00:16:32,590 --> 00:16:34,690
If you have something urgent

264
00:16:34,710 --> 00:16:35,570
that needs my help,

265
00:16:35,880 --> 00:16:36,980
I've thought of a way.

266
00:16:45,310 --> 00:16:46,100
Thank you.

267
00:16:50,190 --> 00:16:51,220
You're welcome.

268
00:16:56,310 --> 00:16:57,100
Good night.

269
00:16:57,120 --> 00:16:57,980
Good night.

270
00:17:24,110 --> 00:17:25,370
So where will I be staying?

271
00:17:36,150 --> 00:17:37,700
Guess you do have some conscience left.

272
00:18:33,110 --> 00:18:34,090
What are you thinking?

273
00:18:38,390 --> 00:18:39,330
These few people

274
00:18:41,920 --> 00:18:44,260
all gave flawless answers
to every question.

275
00:18:45,790 --> 00:18:47,770
Everything seemed just right.

276
00:18:50,440 --> 00:18:52,090
You've been around Xian Biyun so long.

277
00:18:52,110 --> 00:18:54,370
Has she ever mentioned
the proposal to you?

278
00:18:54,590 --> 00:18:55,610
No.

279
00:18:56,040 --> 00:18:57,260
I only found out today myself.

280
00:19:00,920 --> 00:19:02,850
Do you believe today's proposal?

281
00:19:03,310 --> 00:19:04,900
I think

282
00:19:05,830 --> 00:19:06,770
it's believable.

283
00:19:08,150 --> 00:19:09,090
Think about it.

284
00:19:09,960 --> 00:19:11,500
Mr. Lee is British

285
00:19:11,920 --> 00:19:13,090
and wealthy.

286
