00:22:03,760 --> 00:22:06,260
means removing everyone here
from the world of the living.

340
00:22:15,070 --> 00:22:16,330
I can crack it in six days.

341
00:22:17,550 --> 00:22:18,660
Five days should do it.

342
00:22:19,110 --> 00:22:20,050
Three days.

343
00:22:23,870 --> 00:22:24,900
I think

344
00:22:25,920 --> 00:22:27,050
three days is enough.

345
00:22:28,520 --> 00:22:30,130
Alright, three days it is.

346
00:22:30,150 --> 00:22:30,850
Within three days,

347
00:22:30,870 --> 00:22:32,570
Sanyangli will be on lockdown.

348
00:22:32,590 --> 00:22:34,370
I'll be waiting for your good news.

349
00:22:35,280 --> 00:22:35,980
Farewell.

350
00:22:51,240 --> 00:22:52,220
Only three days.

351
00:22:53,240 --> 00:22:55,740
Ms. Xian, would you say
these people are crazy?

352
00:22:56,110 --> 00:22:57,900
I've seen people rushing to find a wife,

353
00:22:57,920 --> 00:22:59,370
never ones rushing to find death.

354
00:22:59,720 --> 00:23:01,460
Yi Xiuyuan isn't rushing to die.

355
00:23:03,110 --> 00:23:04,700
