376
00:24:23,150 --> 00:24:24,130
That won't do.

377
00:24:24,150 --> 00:24:24,610
You can't crack it.

378
00:24:26,280 --> 00:24:28,260
But if you don't crack it,

379
00:24:29,350 --> 00:24:31,890
we'll just be waiting here to die.

380
00:24:33,190 --> 00:24:34,780
I'll find a way to contact Luo Han

381
00:24:35,590 --> 00:24:37,260
and have the Shanghai Bureau
stop sending messages.

382
00:24:38,390 --> 00:24:40,540
Once we confirm the code
has been abandoned,

383
00:24:41,240 --> 00:24:42,810
we can decipher it.

384
00:25:15,960 --> 00:25:16,330
Can't believe it.

385
00:25:18,350 --> 00:25:19,130
What are you doing?

386
00:25:20,760 --> 00:25:21,740
Mr. Lee is having a headache attack.

387
00:25:21,960 --> 00:25:23,060
I need to go out and buy him medicine.

388
00:25:23,080 --> 00:25:23,940
No way.

389
00:25:23,960 --> 00:25:25,330
Director Liang has ordered

390
00:25:25,350 --> 00:25:28,570
no one can get out
from Sanyangli from today.

391
00:26:23,720 --> 00:26:24,570
Captain Amu.

392
00:26:24,960 --> 00:26:25,940
Mr. Lee is having a headache attack.

