414
00:27:16,000 --> 00:27:16,940
Alright?

415
00:27:34,480 --> 00:27:35,410
Here.

416
00:27:38,590 --> 00:27:39,940
Thank you, Captain Amu.

417
00:28:03,670 --> 00:28:04,650
What are you doing?

418
00:28:04,670 --> 00:28:05,780
Delivering newspapers.

419
00:28:05,800 --> 00:28:06,850
Go away.

420
00:28:06,870 --> 00:28:07,890
Sanyangli is on lockdown.

