00:29:41,870 --> 00:29:43,850
they will definitely suspect
Joseph Lee's stance,

450
00:29:43,870 --> 00:29:45,130
especially Liang Jingyuan will.

451
00:29:45,150 --> 00:29:46,300
He's very suspicious.

452
00:29:46,560 --> 00:29:46,940
If you do this,

453
00:29:46,960 --> 00:29:49,060
