00:30:33,190 --> 00:30:35,610
You were the one who insisted on
making Sword Thrust Operation

462
00:30:35,630 --> 00:30:39,300
independent from the Shanghai Bureau.

463
00:30:40,630 --> 00:30:41,500
Now,

464
00:30:41,960 --> 00:30:44,740
you are Gu Yangshan's liaison.

465
00:30:45,910 --> 00:30:47,610
