00:36:52,190 --> 00:36:53,250
Split it fifty-fifty.

556
00:36:54,840 --> 00:36:55,650
Liang.

557
00:36:56,270 --> 00:36:57,020
Mr. Liang.

558
00:36:58,790 --> 00:36:59,730
Director Liang.

559
00:37:01,440 --> 00:37:02,420
Liang, Liang.

560
00:37:03,590 --> 00:37:05,610
